text: Toupin is a surname. Notable people with the name include: *Antoine Toupin or Antoine Becks (born 1981), Canadian-American musician, producer, actor *Felix A. Toupin (1886–1965), American lawyer and politician *Fernand Toupin (1930–2009), Canadian painter *Jack Toupin (1910–1987), Canadian ice hockey player *Jacques Toupin or Jacques Jansen (1913–2002), French opera singer *Marie Aioe Dorion Venier Toupin (c. 1786–1850), member of Pacific Northwest expedition *Marie-Chantal Toupin (born 1971), Canadian musician *Normand Toupin, Canadian politician *Paul Toupin (1918–1993), Canadian journalist, essayist and playwright *Rene Toupin (1934–2014), Canadian politician *Robert Toupin (born 1949), Canadian politician ==See also== *Taupin (surname)
